Water Report

Caz Bell and A.J. Brown

2023-08-21

Introduction

This report details data collected from 2023-01-01 to 2023-08-21 by the Colorado State University (CSU) Agriculture Water Quality Program (AWQP). For more information, please contact AJ Brown at Ansley.Brown@colostate.edu or visit the CSU AWQP Website at https://waterquality.colostate.edu.

Notes

  • All 0 values reported are non-detects (ND) reported by ALS
  • Total suspended solids (TSS), Electrical Conductivity (EC), and pH are performed by AWQP staff at CSU, whereas all other analytes are reported by ALS Laboratories
  • Methods used to derive each analyte can be found in the Raw Data table in the method column
